<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to the Gift of the Givers Foundation</h1>
    <p>
        The Gift of the Givers Foundation is a leading humanitarian organization in South Africa, dedicated to providing
        emergency relief and support to communities affected by natural disasters and crises. Our mission is to alleviate
        suffering and restore dignity through timely and effective assistance.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        Our mission is to deliver humanitarian aid to those in need, ensuring that help reaches those who require it most
        without any discrimination. We operate with compassion, integrity, and resilience, striving to rebuild lives and
        communities after disasters.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Disaster Relief: Rapid response to natural disasters such as floods, earthquakes, and fires.</li>
        <li>Food Security: Provision of essential food supplies to vulnerable communities.</li>
        <li>Health Services: Offering medical aid and healthcare support in crisis situations.</li>
        <li>Education: Initiatives to support education for children affected by disasters.</li>
        <li>Volunteer Programs: Engaging community members to contribute their skills and time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>
        There are many ways you can support our mission:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Donate:</strong> Your contributions help us provide essential services and resources.</li>
        <li><strong>Volunteer:</strong> Join our team of volunteers to make a difference in your community.</li>
        <li><strong>Spread the Word:</strong> Help us raise awareness about our efforts and the needs of affected communities.</li>
    </ul>

